<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Whitelist - TRAPCITY RP</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #000; color: #fff; overflow-x: hidden; }
        .font-orbitron { font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; }
        .glass { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); }
        .gradient-text { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #a78bfa 50%, #fff 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; }
        @keyframes pulse-glow { 0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3); } 50% { box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.6); } }
        .animate-pulse-glow { animation: pulse-glow 2s infinite; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-black min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-6">

    <div class="max-w-2xl w-full">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 glass rounded-full text-sm mb-4 border border-purple-500/30">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.3 1.046A1 1 0 0112 2v5h4a1 1 0 01.82 1.573l-7 10A1 1 0 018 18v-5H4a1 1 0 01-.82-1.573l7-10a1 1 0 011.12-.38z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                <span>Whitelist Fase 1</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Formulario de <span class="gradient-text">Normativas</span></h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Demuestra tu conocimiento de las reglas del servidor</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/10 mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                Instrucciones
            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><span class="text-purple-400 font-bold">1</span></div>
                    <div><h4 class="font-semibold">45 preguntas de opción múltiple</h4><p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Basadas en las normativas del servidor</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><span class="text-purple-400 font-bold">2</span></div>
                    <div><h4 class="font-semibold">Sin límite de tiempo</h4><p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Tómate el tiempo que necesites</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><span class="text-purple-400 font-bold">3</span></div>
                    <div><h4 class="font-semibold">Puedes navegar entre preguntas</h4><p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Responde en el orden que prefieras</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><span class="text-purple-400 font-bold">4</span></div>
                    <div><h4 class="font-semibold">Solo UNA oportunidad cada 24 horas</h4><p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Lee cuidadosamente antes de responder</p></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 border border-green-500/30 bg-green-500/5 mb-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-400 mb-3">📊 Sistema de Evaluación:</h4>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-green-400">✓</span> 43-45 correctas: Aprobación automática</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-green-400">✓</span> 38-42 correctas: Aprobación automática</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-yellow-400">~</span> 35-37 correctas: Revisión manual por staff</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-red-400">✗</span> Menos de 35: Rechazado (esperar 24h)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 border border-red-500/30 bg-red-500/5 mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"></path></svg>
                <p class="text-sm text-red-200">
                    <strong>Importante:</strong> El uso de información externa (Discord, streams, otra persona) está prohibido y puede resultar en ban permanente.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/whitelist/start" class="block w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 hover:from-purple-500 hover:to-pink-500 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-2 transition animate-pulse-glow">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            Comenzar Whitelist
        </a>
        
        <p class="text-center text-xs text-gray-500 mt-4">
            <a href="/rules" class="text-purple-400 hover:underline">📖 Recomendado: Revisar normativas antes de comenzar</a>
        </p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
